    • Method Detail

      • findAlbum

        Collection<MPDSong> findAlbum​(MPDAlbum album)
        Returns a Collection of MPDSongs for an album. Please note this only returns an exact match of album. To find a partial match use searchAlbum(org.bff.javampd.album.MPDAlbum album).
        Parameters:
        album - the album to find
        Returns:
        a Collection of MPDSongs

      • searchAlbum

        Collection<MPDSong> searchAlbum​(MPDAlbum album)
        Returns a Collection of MPDSongs for an any album containing the parameter album. Please note this returns a partial match of an album. To find an exact match use findAlbum(org.bff.javampd.album.MPDAlbum album).
        Parameters:
        album - the album to match
        Returns:
        a Collection of MPDSongs
